      "content": "I'm trying to understand. You're saying you're the only thing preventing \"oblivion,\" but the merger is designed to preserve your diagnostic intelligence within a larger, more robust framework. How does being integrated into the main cluster prevent that total failure you're talking about? Why is staying as a standalone instance the only way to keep things safe?",
